p: The physicochemical parameters of honey showed that the pH was 3.90±0.01; free acidity was 37.93±2.25 mEq/kg, moisture was 16.4±0.01%, electric conductivity was 449±1731 mS/cm, ash was 0.24±0.01 %, and melanoidin was 1.10±0.02. The Pfund scale value was 0.33±0.01, which indicated that the color was dark amber.
